flowchart TD
    Start([Tenant Admin opens Papermite]) --> HasModel{Active model\nexists?}

    %% No model path
    HasModel -- No --> Upload[Upload Document\nPDF / DOCX / TXT]
    Upload --> Parse[Docling parses document\nto structured text]
    Parse --> Extract[AI extracts entities\nStudent, Guardian, Program, etc.]
    Extract --> Consolidate[Consolidate duplicate\nentity types]
    Consolidate --> InferType[Infer field types\ndate, email, phone, selection, etc.]
    InferType --> Review

    %% Has model path
    HasModel -- Yes --> ModelCard[View Active Model\nversion, timestamp, updated-by]
    ModelCard --> EditOrUpload{User action}
    EditOrUpload -- Edit Model --> LoadModel[Load model into\nReview page]
    LoadModel --> Review
    EditOrUpload -- Upload New Doc --> Upload

    %% Review
    Review[Review & Customize\nEdit values, types, required flags\nAdd/remove fields, define selection options]
    Review --> Changed{Changes\ndetected?}
    Changed -- No --> StayReview[Finalize button disabled\nModify fields to continue]
    StayReview --> Review
    Changed -- Yes --> Finalize[Finalize Model]

    %% Finalize
    Finalize --> Preview[Preview\nDry run — no DB write]
    Preview --> Unchanged{Model unchanged\nfrom active?}
    Unchanged -- Yes --> NoChange[No Changes Detected\nNo new version created]
    NoChange --> Landing
    Unchanged -- No --> ConfirmPage[Show entity summary\nwith sample data + JSON preview]
    ConfirmPage --> Decision{User decision}
    Decision -- Cancel --> Landing
    Decision -- Confirm & Save --> Commit[Store in LanceDB\nArchive previous version\nIncrement version number\nTrim if > 50 versions]
    Commit --> Landing([Landing Page\nwith updated model])

    style Start fill:#CF8A2E,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style Landing fill:#CF8A2E,color:#fff,stroke:none
